## Testing

```bash
deno test libs/firecat-protocol/confirmation_test.ts
```

Tests should:
1. Seed a valid pending envelope
2. Run one poll cycle
3. Verify attestation was written
4. Run another poll cycle and verify 0 new processing (already attested)
5. Seed an invalid pending envelope
6. Run poll and verify rejection was written with correct reason

## Dependencies

Depends on G2-A2-01 (validators), G2-A2-03 (pending markers must exist in the system), G2-A2-04 (validator set for authorization). Uses cursor pattern from G2-A1-02. Blocks G2-A2-07 (finalization) and G2-E1-02 (multi-node confirmation testing).
